{"tid":650464,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"好蠢幫老細慳錢","createTime":"2018-05-02T11:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T12:12:20.000Z","uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"002a791c10bb76f61789359493e341f2011df9d9","tid":650464,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"份工老母朋友介紹既<br />\n本生同老細食飯deal左12k<br />\n食完佢send份application form比我<br />\n到今日返工簽contract發現得11600<br />\n原來自己on9填form將expected salary 填左自己上份人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有問過佢，佢一開始應該冇醒起係我填錯<br />\n話我未過probation 過左會加返12k up比我<br />\n我再話原來我填錯左<br />\n佢就話 係呀 你填11599架麻<br />\n我係咪冇可能fight得返個四舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔多 但個心唔太舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係好撚蠢點解咁都填錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050a54309b5314fce6d2b4c22e99d993d1225830","tid":650464,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32fa27a29e7d78ebda5a93eeb8e48a30001fda6","tid":650464,"uid":117896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"你講佢唔撚撈"},{"pid":"ce1f20719dc1e4d2493f0426e52dd6365b7b6679","tid":650464,"uid":175112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"真係好蠢。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6386bc04bcee6ce049cb5cd44752ed5372f367","tid":650464,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1f20719dc1e4d2493f0426e52dd6365b7b6679","tid":650464,"uid":175112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"真係好蠢。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smi